text: Kristina Panayotova (born 27 August 1975) is a Bulgarian gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sofia
